import pandas as pd

se1 = pd.read_table("salmon_output_DRR100656/quant.sf")
se1 = se1.drop(columns=['Length', 'EffectiveLength', 'NumReads'])
se1.columns = ['Name', 'TPM_DRR100656']
se2 = pd.read_table("salmon_output_DRR100657/quant.sf")
se2 = se2.drop(columns=['Length', 'EffectiveLength', 'NumReads'])
se2.columns = ['Name', 'TPM_DRR100657']

se = pd.merge(e1, e2, on='Name')
se.head()

%matplotlib inline
import seaborn as sns

ax = sns.scatterplot(x="TPM_DRR100656", y="TPM_DRR100657", data=se)

import numpy as np

se['log_DRR100656'] = np.log10(se['TPM_DRR100656'] + 1)
se['log_DRR100657'] = np.log10(se['TPM_DRR100657'] + 1)
se['diff'] = abs(se['TPM_DRR100656'] - se['TPM_DRR100657'])

#ax = sns.scatterplot(x='log_DRR100656', y='log_DRR100657', data=se)

# 
sns.regplot(x='log_DRR100656', y='log_DRR100657', data=se, scatter_kws={'color': 'steelblue'}, line_kws={'color': 'orange'})

ke1 = pd.read_table("DRR100656_kallisto_out/abundance.tsv")
ke1 = ke1.drop(columns=['length', 'eff_length', 'est_counts'])
ke1.columns = ['Name', 'TPM_DRR100656']
ke2 = pd.read_table("DRR100657_kallisto_out/abundance.tsv")
ke2 = ke2.drop(columns=['length', 'eff_length', 'est_counts'])
ke2.columns = ['Name', 'TPM_DRR100657']

ke = pd.merge(ke1, ke2, on='Name')
ke['log_DRR100656'] = np.log10(ke['TPM_DRR100656'] + 1)
ke['log_DRR100657'] = np.log10(ke['TPM_DRR100657'] + 1)

#ax = sns.scatterplot(x='log_DRR100656', y='log_DRR100657', data=ke)

# 
ax = sns.regplot(x='log_DRR100656', y='log_DRR100657', data=ke, scatter_kws={'color': 'steelblue'}, line_kws={'color': 'orange'})

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

fig = plt.figure()
ax2 = fig.add_subplot(1,1,1)
ax2.scatter(x='log_DRR100656', y='log_DRR100657', label='salmon',  data=se, color='red', marker='.', alpha=0.8)
ax2.scatter(x='log_DRR100656', y='log_DRR100657', label='kallisto', data=ke, color='steelblue', marker='x', alpha=0.8)

a, b = np.polyfit(se['log_DRR100656'], se['log_DRR100657'], 1)

#ax2.grid(True)
ax2.legend()
